==English==

===Pronunciation===
*kämə, /kaːmə/, /ka:m@/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-aːmə|Rhymes: -aːmə]]

===Etymology===
From Japanese [[鎌]] ([[かま]], kama), ''[[sickle]]'', ''[[scythe]]''.

===Noun===
'''kama''' (''plural:'' '''kama''' or [[kamas]])

#a [[sickle]]-like weapon, originally used as a tool for cutting weeds.


